Class PrettyPrinter

  • java.lang.Object
    • IC.AST.PrettyPrinter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Visitor

    public class PrettyPrinter
extends java.lang.Object
implements Visitor
    Pretty printing visitor - travels along the AST and prints info about each node, in an easy-to-comprehend format.
    Author:
    Tovi Almozlino
